de.charite.compbio.jannovar.cmd.annotate_vcf

Class AnnotatedVariantWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.charite.compbio.jannovar.cmd.annotate_vcf.AnnotatedVariantWriter
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AnnotatedJannovarWriter, AnnotatedVCFWriter

    public abstract class AnnotatedVariantWriter
extends Object
    Interface for output writers in Jannovar class. The task of such a writer is to take a HTSJDK annotation, perform annotation with the Jannovar code and then write it out into some output format. Currently, we have to convert HTSJDK VariantContext objects into Jannovar Variant objects but that should be simplified later on.
    Author:
    Manuel Holtgrewe
